                    |                                                    |
                    |                                                    |
  +\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-+\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-+                       |
  |                 |                            v                       v
+\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-+     +\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-+     +\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-+     +\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-+     +\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-+
| /bin/bash | \-\-> | /lib/libncurses.so.5 | \-\-> | /lib/libdl.so.2 | \-\-> | /lib/libc.so.6 | \-\-> | ld\-linux.so.2 |
